p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/97596fcdaf6da8e4.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"453\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 453px; rwidth: 400px;\" id=\"20140513_45/isuhani_1399970423260UuL0u_JPEG/5.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7E00FCC')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/97596fcdaf6da8e4.jpg\"></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">유전적인 요인도 성장부진의 원인이 될 수 있지만 소아비만, 질병, 척추측만 등으로 인한 후천적인 요인도 무시할 </span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>수 없습니다.</span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>대부분의 아이들은 정상적인 체중과 키로 태어나지만 자라면서 키 </span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>차이가 많이 나게 되는 이유는 무엇일까요</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>?</span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>키가 크는 시기는 대개 정해져 있는데</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>,</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'> 그 시기에 적절한 치료를 받지 </span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>않으면 제대로 된 성장을 할 수 없습니다</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: HY강B; font-size: 14pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;\"> </span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><u><strong><img src=\"https://ssl.pstatic.net/static.se2/static/full/20130612/emoticon/3_12.gif\" onload=\"setTimeout('utility.resizeImageWithId(\\'static\\/full\\/20130612\\/emoticon\\/3_12.gif\\')',200)\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"static/full/20130612/emoticon/3_12.gif\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7E00FCC')\" alt=\"\">&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><u>성장치료, 언제하는 것이 좋을까요?</u></span></strong></u><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>☞ 출생 ~ 만3세</span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>잔병치레를 많이 하거나</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>, </span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>먹는\r\n것이 부실하다면 성장에 문제가 생길 수 </span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>있습니다</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>이 시기에 평균키로 만들어 주지 못하면 그 이후에는 따라잡기가 아주 </span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>어려워지고 또래에 비해 작은&nbsp;키를 가지게 되는 것이죠</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; unicode-bidi: embed; direction: ltr; language: ko; mso-line-break-override: none; punctuation-wrap: hanging;\"><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>너무 이른 시기에 성장치료를 하는 것이 아닌지 걱정이 되겠지만</span><span style='color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'> </span><u style=\"text-underline: single;\"><span style='color: red; font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; font-weight: bold; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>사실은</span></u><u style=\"text-underline: single;\"><span style='color: red; font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; font-weight: bold; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>만</span></u><u style=\"text-underline: single;\"><span style='color: red; font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; font-weight: bold; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>3</span></u><u style=\"text-underline: single;\"><span style='color: red; font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; font-weight: bold; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>세까지의 성장이\r\n가장 중요합니다</span></u><u style=\"text-underline: single;\"><span style='color: red; font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; font-weight: bold; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>.</span></u></p><p>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">☞ 만3세 이후 ~ 사춘기 이전</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>유치원 혹은 학교에서 단체생활을 하기 때문에 다양한 질병에 쉽게 </span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>노출되면서 성장을 하게 됩니다</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>비염</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>, </span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>아토피가 있거나 </span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>1</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>년에 평균 </span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>4cm</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>미만으로 자란다면</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'> 치료를 꾸준히 </span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>하는 것이 좋습니다</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>.</span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'><strong><u>☞ 두번째 급성장기 \"사춘기\"</u></strong></span></p><span style='color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>남자가 여자보다 키가 큰 이유는 사춘기가 여자보다 늦기 때문입니다</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>사춘기가 오는 시기는 여자 평균 </span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>10</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>세</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>, </span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>남자는\r\n</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>11.6</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>세로 이 사춘기를</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>기준으로 남녀 다같이 키가 부쩍부쩍 자라게 됩니다</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140513_44/isuhani_13999704385505Po7G_JPEG/7.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"213\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 213px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140513_44/isuhani_13999704385505Po7G_JPEG/7.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7E00FCC')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140513_44/isuhani_13999704385505Po7G_JPEG/7.jpg?type=w3\"></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p></span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>사춘기는 체지방과 관련이 있습니다</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>. </span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>체지방이\r\n많다면 사춘기는 더 </span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>빨리 올 수도 있다는 것이지요</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>. </span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>이것을\r\n</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>성조숙증이라고</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'> 합니다</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'>소아비만은 다양한 성인병의 위험성도 문제지만 </span><u><strong><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; background-color: rgb(255, 239, 0); language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'><u>성조숙증이</u></span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; background-color: rgb(255, 239, 0); language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'><u> 생기면 </u></span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; background-color: rgb(255, 239, 0); language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'><u>키도 덜\r\n클 수 있다는 사실을 명심해야 합니다</u></span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt; background-color: rgb(255, 239, 0); language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;'><u>.</u></span></strong></u><span style=\"color: red; font-family: HY강B; font-size: 14pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: HY강B; mso-fareast-font-family: HY강B; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt;\">\r\n</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;</p></span><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp